\begin_layout Standard
This treatment was implemented using short, engaging videos, shown to the
 farmers on tablet computers.
 Video's featuring role models have been found effective in changing people's
 behaviour in a range of applications 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "van2021information,10.1162/rest_a_01153,bernard2015will"
literal "false"

\end_inset

.
